            <li>Heading anchors generated through a plugin.</li>
            <li>Task list markers turned into disabled checkboxes.</li>
            <li>External links opened in a new tab with safe rel attributes.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="meta-card">
          <h2>Source</h2>
          <pre class="source">{source}</pre>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
